                <listAnnotation xml:lang="en" type="notes">
                    
                        <note n="1" xml:id="note-t-1">
                            

<p>The news was that on 1 January 1873 Theo was to start work at the Brussels branch of the art dealer Goupil &amp; Co., 58 rue Montagne de la Cour (Hofbergstraat).</p>
                        </note>
                        
                    
                        <note n="2" xml:id="note-t-2">
                            

<p>Van Gogh worked as an assistant at the Hague branch of Goupil &amp; Co. located at Plaats 14. </p>
                        </note>
                        
                            

                        
                    
